<span style="font-weight: bold">The Statute gives ICJ juristiction over crimes commited in the US by US citizens.</span> Any which way the wind blows in the UN the ICJ would be a tool for enforcing whatever law they want in the US.  Potentially and with great probablitiy US domestic affairs would be manipulated by foreign powers through this facade of justice.
<br />

