In addition the following garuntees of civil protection in the US constitution would be deprecated and potentially supplanted if the ICJ had jusristiction in the US:
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Article I - Section 9:
