The big lie in every site I ran into that was por ratification made this outright lie in exactly the same way:
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">The US claims that the ICC potentially could investigate and try US citizens without US consent even though the US is not a party to the ICC Statute.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
