Are you speaking of removal politically or socially?  Socially is what I'm referring to.  I vote for the judges here in my city and state also, but as far as representing my interests?  Not hardly.  None of them do, really.  They're far too conservative.  It's an extremely rare person who is similar enough to you to accurately represent your interests, and judges are no exception to that rule.
<br />

<br />
Now politically?  Yes, they're much, much farther removed than judges here in the U.S.
<br />

<br />
Flarestar Bladesinger<br />
